mb30">Salzburg</placeName><date when="1920-07-30" n="01">30. 7. 1920</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02351">Schnitzler an Adam, 20. 7. 1922</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02353">Schnitzler an Brandes, 16. 8. 1920</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02347">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 10. 7. 1920</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02364">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [19. 3. 1921]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
